FBIS3-1607 "drchi039_f_94018" FBIS-CHI-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 Near East & South Asia PRC `Appreciates' Signing of Yemen Accord OW2802094794 Beijing XINHUA in English 0911 GMT 28 Feb 94 OW2802094794 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, February 28 (XINHUA) -- A Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman said here today that China appreciates a reconciliation accord recently signed by the leaders of Yemen. The spokesman said this when commenting on the accord that was reportedly signed. "The Chinese Government appreciates the signing of a reconciliation accord by the leaders of Yemen," the spokesman said, adding that China sincerely hopes that Yemen will enjoy stability and economic development and that its people lead a happy life.
